<table border="0" cellpadding="5" width="550" cellspacing="5" height="400" >
<tr valign="top" height="400" >
<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><i style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br>(Use for those who notified us)<br></font></i><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Thank you for the time on the phone earlier, I am sorry to learn of the claim being made against you.<br></span><i style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>(Use for those where we received notification)<br></i><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">We have received notification of a potential claim being made against you for <i>(insert allegations and claimant here)</i>.<br></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>As discussed, in order that I can register the claim with insurers, please could you forward me the following:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Overview of events to date leading up to the claim</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">The date of when the incident occurred and when the claim was made against you</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Description of the injury sustained by your employee</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Copy of any contract/emails with your employee</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of the job your employee was to undertake</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Invoice/charge sheet for the work undertaken by your employee</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Confirmation of your VAT status</font></li></ul><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">I attach your policy schedule and wording to assist.<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Upon receipt of the above, I will send to our insurers for review. Depending on how quickly you return the information will determine the timeframe for this.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>I look forward to hearing from you.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Claims Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: claims@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>